PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of CHRISTIANE OUIMET, of Orléans, Ontario, as a director of Queens Quay West Land Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Jane Billings, whose term has expired.
